    "description": "Glurp为你呈献疯狂派对游戏<br><br>“再来一口Glurp”是一款集运动、搞怪物理机制、派对性于一体的多人热座游戏。背景设置在天外之境，这里的外星人山寨了地球的夏季奥运会。但这个山寨版奥运会处处让人啼笑皆非。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/3c00f135487ae2abc7c8ed74d29b0a44.poster.avif?t=1724771936\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/3c00f135487ae2abc7c8ed74d29b0a44.webm?t=1724771936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/3c00f135487ae2abc7c8ed74d29b0a44.mp4?t=1724771936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>外星人们在狂刷地球节目“瞬间看地球”以后，觉得体育赛事里面少不了广告环节！ 赞助商能随机控制赛事，并根据自己的喜好更改规则，势将夏季运动会搞得乌七八糟。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与朋友家人同乐</h2>你能以各种异想天开的形式助跑、跳跃、投掷，与 20 名本地玩家在派对模式中比赛狂欢；你可以通过单人挑战模式，完成一系列艰难挑战，勇攀排行榜巅峰。 你也可以看着朋友们玩得东摇西晃，或者向他们偷师学艺。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/8cb640a703dbb356ceb6e88984582e40.poster.avif?t=1724771936\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/8cb640a703dbb356ceb6e88984582e40.webm?t=1724771936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/8cb640a703dbb356ceb6e88984582e40.mp4?t=1724771936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多内容！</h2>数不清的比赛和赞助商，使“Glurp”玩法层出不穷。在一场比赛中上手后，你就会得到激光手！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我最摇摆！</h2>“Glurp”是一款老少皆宜的刺激游戏，随时让你欢呼连连、玩不释手！此款游戏使用加入/退出和延迟上场功能确保持续操作。 只需一个手柄就能乐翻天。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/9d73c251b0e9e9f7d0137f32736d35c6.poster.avif?t=1724771936\" width=700 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/9d73c251b0e9e9f7d0137f32736d35c6.webm?t=1724771936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1056690/extras/9d73c251b0e9e9f7d0137f32736d35c6.mp4?t=1724771936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩出风格！</h2>运动员的每一只手臂都可以通过手柄操纵杆独立控制。你可以抓取控制每只手臂......就是这么简单！掌控自己的游戏风格并设计独特的玩法技巧，在游戏中立于不败之地！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>派对模式支持本地2-20名玩家多人游戏<br></li><li>数千个赛事和赞助商组合<br></li><li>每次玩都有新挑战<br></li><li>具有在线排行榜和重玩的单人挑战模式<br></li><li>搞怪物理机制<br></li><li>更多“Glurp”现已上线</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现在，有请我们的赞助商发言</h2><strong>炫彩颜色，零级口味</strong><br> <br><strong>再来一口GLURP</strong><br> <br>一口“Glurp”，超群表现。炫彩颜色，零级口味，“Glurp”让运动员赢在起跑线。<br><br><br>*******************<br><br><br>PC Gamer<br>“The soundtrack of Drink More Glurp is the hoots and gasps of your friends, and when someone figures out a new trick, or overcomes the seemingly impossible, the mood is absolutely electric.”<br><br>EDGE magazine<br>“We can see this becoming a party favourite” “The sponsorship structure is a stroke of brilliance.”<br><br>RockPaperShotgun<br>“When I won a round, I chugged my whole can of glurp and loosed a dreadful, ululating bellow like a wookie”<br><br>Kotaku UK<br>“Simple concepts matched with a constantly changing rulebook make this an outstanding party game.”",
